{"title":"耕牛的蹄印","authors":["青勃"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":1,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕牛的蹄印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青勃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田野上走着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在平整的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在松软的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了深深的蹄印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的春天已经来临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湿润的田野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛被牵出牛屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在下过一场牛毛细雨以后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在桃酥一样酥散的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"印下了深深的蹄印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国开始了新的耕耘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湿润的田野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼了满地珍珠似的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野是农民的一片织锦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机唱着钢铁的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕牛摇曳着铃铛的谣曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你背上没有猛抽的鞭子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹄下再不见泥淖、荆棘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拖着沉重的犁轭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一个脚印地走着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土翻滚着棕褐色的波浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在坚韧地开垦黑土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁到地头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该歇一歇了，喘一喘气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你象一架山卧在犁沟里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田边摇摆着嫩柳的长辫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃花探出了一脸红晕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚梳理好羽毛的喜鹊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞上了你的脊背"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉静地歇卧在牧歌里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为土地劳累的老黄牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石兽一样静卧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠实于泥土的老黄牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你呆滞的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淳朴的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"审视着你的蹄印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这深深的蹄窝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你浑身的力气所夯下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是沉重的叹息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是爱情的标记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这深深的蹄窝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你对祖国的贡献"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象在四化征途上的炎黄子孙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种的深的浅的踪迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象拖拉机在广阔的田野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种的爱的辙印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也象诗人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在稿纸的田格里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获的诚实的诗句"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}